{"tid":607370,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鍾情日本廚刀","createTime":"2018-03-27T08:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T10:12:58.000Z","uid":55377,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"50222698dd6cf172230ee408dfe0d02b12c0044b","tid":607370,"uid":55377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T08:57:14.000Z","msg":"小弟唔係專業廚師，閒時喜歡煮下野食切下野。<br />\n機緣巧合下接觸到日本廚刀，可能因為以前讀書果陣接觸得多鋼材，加上日本刀既design 真係靚過西廚刀太多，搞到而家中哂毒。<br />\n好在自己對carbon steel冇乜興趣,唔係既話真係破產都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我先拋磚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/164926_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F164926_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=60d7c52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/164933_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F164933_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3f459f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/164942_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F164942_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=061c9dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/164951_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F164951_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=446cae81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/164818_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbna